    .container.PostWrapper

      .col-md-12.PostHeadline
        h1 About us

      .col-md-6.PostContent
        p ALL4YOU Overseas Education Consulting, providing consulting services related to training opportunities abroad, is a well-established organization. Our organization is the official representative  of  higher education  institutions providing education in English in Hungary, the Czech Republic, Slovakia, Bulgaria, Croatia, Romania and Serbia, as well as Austrian and German universities.

      .col-md-6.PostContent
        p ALL4YOU Overseas Education Consultancy is a dynamic family institution  with   its  long standing experience in  Hungary, Slovakia, the Czech Republic, Bulgaria, Latvia, Lithuania, Estonia, Austria, Germany, Croatia, Romania and Serbia and its aim is to provide you reliable support. It is our priority to please the students who will be trained in the countries in Europe that we have close heart and blood ties.

